Compliance Module Specification v1.0

Module Code: MOD-COMPLIANCE
Priority: Critical MVP
Version: 1.0
Frontend: Flutter + BLoC
Backend: NestJS
Dependencies: Girvi Module, Customer Module, Interest Engine, Reports Module, Notification Module, Audit Module

⸻

1. Module Purpose

The Compliance Module ensures that all lending operations comply with:

* Maharashtra Money-Lending (Regulation) Act
* RBI Gold Loan Guidelines
* KFS (Key Fact Statement) Requirements
* Customer Disclosure Requirements
* Auction Regulations
* Gold Return Obligations
* Audit Requirements

This module automatically generates regulatory forms and monitors compliance violations.

