6. Core Business Rules

BR-COMP-001

Every Girvi requires KFS.

BR-COMP-002

Every active Girvi must appear in Form 11.

BR-COMP-003

Every transaction must appear in Form 12.

BR-COMP-004

Auction notice mandatory before auction.

BR-COMP-005

LTV violations must block loan creation.

BR-COMP-006

Compliance records are immutable.

BR-COMP-007

Generated forms cannot be edited.

BR-COMP-008

All forms require audit logging.

