9. LTV Compliance Engine

Purpose

Prevent RBI violations.

⸻

Formula

LTV = \frac{Loan\ Amount}{Valuation} \times 100

⸻

Rules

Loan Range	Maximum LTV
≤ ₹2.5 Lakh	85%
₹2.5–₹5 Lakh	80%
> ₹5 Lakh	75%

⸻

Violations

Hard Block

No contract creation.

Audit Entry

Mandatory.

